nl.bioinf.diseasefinderSpring.disease

Class Disease

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.bioinf.diseasefinderSpring.disease.Disease
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class Disease
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    Disease collects all the information about one disease which is found. The toString method and summary method of this class print html, so the servlets can use this output.
